{"TopicId":219077,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.12.x] Better Screen Messages","CreatedByName":"UltraJohn","CreatedById":15008,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-30T20:05:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"UltraJohn","CreatedById":15008,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-30T20:05:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:22px;\u0022\u003EBetter Screen Messages\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a small plugin that allows you to move the screen message boxes. This is quite useful if you\u0027re having the problem of the messages being obscured by other UI elements, or if you\u0027re playing at ultrawide resolutions and don\u0027t want to break your neck trying to read the text. You can also change the font size used. Keep in mind that both the position and size are dependent on UI scale value as well!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe position and font size is configurable via\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Esettings.cfg\u003C/strong\u003E file.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EBefore/After preview:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBefore:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022uO5f8G8.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002292.67\u0022 height=\u0022520\u0022 title=\u0022\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/uO5f8G8.jpeg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022XEIwII5.jpeg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002292.67\u0022 height=\u0022520\u0022 title=\u0022\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/XEIwII5.jpeg